    dc:creator "Katwate, Unmesh; Kumkar, Pradeep; Raghavan, Rajeev; Dahanukar, Neelesh" ;
    dc:date "2018" ;
    dc:title "A new syntopic species of small barb from the Western Ghats of India (Teleostei: Cyprinidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456112>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456116>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456114>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456110>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456118>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456120> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456112>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pethia sahit holotype (BNHS FwF 532, 30.6 mm SL). (a) In life, photographed immediately after collection, (b) in preservation, and (c) schematic drawing showing distribution of humeral and caudal spot (outlined and filled gray), lateralline scale row, transverse and intercalated adjacent scale row (filled with diagonal lines)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1456112/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456116>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Male and female of the syntopic species Pethia sahit and P. longicauda. (A) Male and (B) female of P. sahit. (C) Male and (D) female of P. longicauda." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1456116/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456114>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Lateral view of cleared and double stained specimen of (a) Pethia sahit, paratype, male, BNHS FwF 535, 30.6 mm SL and (b) P. longicauda, male, BNHS FwF 542, 31.9 mm SL, collected in syntopy from upstream of Hiranyakeshi River at Ghatkarwadi. Abbreviations: AF, anal fin; CF, caudal fin; DF, dorsal fin; En, epineural intermusculars; Ep, epipleural intermusculars; Nc, neurocranium; PF, pectoral fin; VF, pelvic/ventral fin; weV, weberian vertebrae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1456114/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456110>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Type locality and distribution of Pethia sahit and P. longicauda in the northern part of the Western Ghats of India. Star indicates the type locality of the species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1456110/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456118>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Habitat shared by Pethia sahit and P. longicauda. (a) Habitat at the type locality of P. sahit in Hiranyakeshi River, near Ghatkarwadi and (b) Syntopic occurrence of both species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1456118/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1456120>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Phylogenetic position of Pethia sahit and P. longicauda based on maximum likelihood analysis based on best partition scheme. Values along the nodes are percent bootstraps for 1000 iterations. Species of Garra are used as the out-group." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1456120/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

